DESCRIPTION:[Podcast: This Week in Virology]\n\nIn his weekly clinical upd
 ate\, Dr. Griffin and Vincent Racaniello discuss several states and the go
 vernor of Pennsylvania suing HHS over changes in the childhood vaccination
  schedule\, the vaccine derived type 2 poliovirus outbreak in Pakistan and
  implications for the global withdrawal of the oral poliovirus vaccine\, a
 nd the outbreak of Candida\, then Dr. Griffin deep dives into recent stati
 stics RSV\, influenza and SARS-CoV-2 infections\, the Wasterwater Scan das
 hboard\, Johns Hopkins measles tracker\, where to find PEMGARDA\, how to a
 ccess and pay for Paxlovid\, when to use steroids for treating influenza\,
  long COVID treatment center\, where to go for answers to your long COVID 
 questions\, and contacting your federal government representative to stop 
 the assault on science and biomedical research. Click arrow to play Downlo
