  the Attorney General\, California) 3:00 Surgeon General Nominee Sidesteps
  Questions on Vaccines at Senate Hearing (NY Times) 3:23 Unqualified failu
 re in polio vaccine policy left thousands of kids paralyzed (Science) 13:2
 5 Clinical and Epidemiological Investigation of Vaccine-Derived Poliovirus
  Type 2 Outbreak in Pakistan During 2019–2021 (CID) 8:32 Inactivated Pol
 io Vaccine Must Be \n\nEvent URL: https://www.microbe.tv/twiv/twiv-1300/\n
