DTEND:20260401T131500Z
DTSTAMP:20260329T062558Z
UID:c622b9b3fd44f489@gid-seminars.wnprc.wisc.edu
CATEGORIES:WHO
DESCRIPTION:Influenza\, COVID‑19 and other respiratory pathogens continu
 e to impose a significant global health burden\, requiring sustained vigil
 ance and coordinated action. This session supports WHO’s mandate by faci
 litating the dissemination of evidence‑based updates\, strengthening ali
